            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "No worries, thanks for followup. We should probably detect this situation and show a message. It is often confusing and requires a lot of troubleshooting.\n\n## Proposal\n\n- similar to https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/27537 , detect when NVIM_LOG_FILE (including its default fallback location, if NVIM_LOG_FILE was not set by the user), is inaccessible\n- show an error message\n\nnote: do not ask how to do this. review https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/27537 to see all the details and edge cases that should be handled. PRs that don't do that will be closed.",
