            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Iam still working on it, but feel free to work on it if you want or help get #38070 merged.\n\n it is currently reproducible on master. \nsteps to reproduce: \n```bash\nmkdir -p /tmp/fakenvim\nchmod 000 /tmp/fakenvim\nexport XDG_STATE_HOME=/tmp/fakenvim\nnvim --clean\n``` \nthis will start logging in $CWD \n\nwhat we are trying to get done is to notify the user when either $NVIM_LOG_FILE Environment variable or $XDG_STATE_HOME is inaccessible. \n\nyou can take a look at my pr #38070 and justinmk's comment on it for more context.",
